      <agency>Sanofi</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Sanofi</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this survey on this registered product is to confirm the efficacy, and
      safety profile of Lantus in every day medical practice. This program will also help to obtain
      information about the use of the insulin titration regimen and handling of the Lantus insulin
      analogue.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
